&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN class=292541702-11112004&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN class=292541702-11112004&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;This is a particularly large issue that I didn't have time to get to this time around, primarily because it's going to require extra-special care to ensure that we don't introduce any profitability exploits. Fear not! It's still on the list and has even moved up a rank or two.&lt;IMG height=16 src="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-happy.gif" width=16 border=0&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
